BIB                 10         21
TITLE      Cross section measurements for the 6Li(p,alpha)3He
           reaction in the proton energy range 1.0 - 2.6 MeV
AUTHOR     (Chia-Shou Lin,Wan-Shou Hou,Min Wen,Jen-Chang Chou)
REFERENCE  (J,NP/A,275,93,1977)
INSTITUTE  (3CHFSHI)
FACILITY   (VDG,3CHFSHI)
SAMPLE     (3-LI-6,ENR=0.9603) Lithium fluoride (96.03% in 6Li)
           onto a carbon backing of about 35 ug/cm2. The
           thickness of the 6LiF in the targets was 110+-5 ug/cm2
METHOD     (COINC,PHD)
DETECTOR   (SIBAR) 500 um silicon surface barrier detectors
ERR-ANALYS (ERR-1) Uncertainty in target thickness
           (ERR-2) Errors in current integrator calibration
           (ERR-3) Errors in solid angle measurements
HISTORY    (19800820C) Compilation produced by RFNC-VNIIEF Sarov
           (19990323U)CNPD: corrected 4-dig. year and lower cases.
           (20130130A) Missing value was added in Sub.004 for
           Data-section-SB
           (20180429A) SD: REACTION code corrected in Subents
           002,003. BIB, ERR-ANALYS were updated.
           (20260318U) SD: Small corrections in all Subents.
ENDBIB              21
